'''克里斯蒂·林恩·诺姆'''（{{lang-en|Kristi Lynn Noem}}；{{IPAc-en|n|oʊ|m}}，{{bd|1971年|11月30日}}）是一名[[美国|美国]]政治家，自2019年1月5日起担任[[南达科他州|南达科他州]]{{le|南达科他州州长列表|List of governors of South Dakota|第33任}}{{le|南达科他州州长|Governor of South Dakota|州长}}。作为[[共和党_(美国)|共和党]]成员，她在2011年至2019年间担任[[南达科他州单一国会选区|南达科他州单一国会选区]]的[[美国众议院|众议院]]代表，2007年至2011年担任[[南达科他州众议院|南达科他州众议院]]议员。诺姆在{{le|2018年南达科他州州长选举|2018 South Dakota gubernatorial election}}中当选州长，是南达科他州首位女性州长。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Mitchell |first1=Trevor J. |url=https://www.argusleader.com/story/news/2020/04/01/coronavirus-why-gov-noem-wont-order-shelter-place-south-dakotans/5106939002/ |title=Why Gov. Noem won't order a shelter-in-place for South Dakotans |accessdate=2020-11-21 |work=Argus Leader |date=2020-04-01 |location=Sioux Falls, South Dakota |archive-date=2020-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116193207/https://www.argusleader.com/story/news/2020/04/01/coronavirus-why-gov-noem-wont-order-shelter-place-south-dakotans/5106939002/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==早年生活和教育==
克里斯蒂·诺姆出生于[[南达科他州|南达科他州]][[沃特敦_(南达科他州)|沃特敦]]，与兄弟姐妹一起在[[哈姆林县_(南达科他州)|哈姆林县]]农村的家庭牧场和农场长大<ref name="HeadOfClass"/>。她有[[挪威|挪威]]血统<ref>{{cite tweet |last=Noem |first=Kristi |user=govkristinoem |number=939525185149067267 |date=2017-12-09 |title=Uff-da!! Thank you Graysen for my awesome sweatshirt. As a proud Norwegian I have so many... |language=en |access-date=2020-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116193219/https://twitter.com/govkristinoem/status/939525185149067267 |archive-date=2020-11-16 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。诺姆于1990年毕业于哈姆林高中，并获得了南达科他州雪之女王（South Dakota Snow Queen）的称号。 她认为自己的经验可以帮助她提高公开演讲和宣传技巧<ref name="title meant"/>。高中毕业后，她就读于{{le|北方州立大学|Northern State University}}。 她在20岁时与布莱恩·诺姆（Bryon Noem）结婚<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://siouxcityjournal.com/news/local/a1/kristi-noem-a-fit-for-the-times-as-she-takes/article_b11d9663-5eca-56a2-b122-9d9fc512f935.html|title=Kristi Noem a 'fit for the times' as she takes office|last=Hayworth|first=Bret|work=Sioux City Journal|access-date=2020-11-21|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116193208/https://siouxcityjournal.com/news/local/a1/kristi-noem-a-fit-for-the-times-as-she-takes/article_b11d9663-5eca-56a2-b122-9d9fc512f935.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

22岁时，诺姆在父亲死于一场农机事故后离开了大学，帮助经营她家的牧场<ref name="HeadOfClass"/><ref name="poignant"/>。诺姆在这片土地上增加了一个狩猎小屋和一家餐馆，她的所有兄弟姐妹都搬回来帮助扩大业务。<ref name="HeadOfClass"/>

在她父亲去世后，诺姆停止全日制大学学习，但之后在{{le|马蒂山学院|Mount Marty University}}沃特敦校区和[[南达科他州立大学|南达科他州立大学]]上课，并在[[南达科他大学|南达科他大学]]在线学习课程。<ref name="HeadOfClass"/><ref name="title meant"/>

当选国会议员后，诺姆继续她的教育，参加在线课程。[[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]]称她是国会山“最有影响力的实习生”，因为她从国会议员的职位上获得了大学实习生学分<ref>{{cite news|last=Heil|first=Emily|title=Kristy Noem: Capitol Hill's most powerful intern|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/in-the-loop/post/kristy-noem-capitol-hills-most-powerful-intern/2012/01/19/gIQAhujsAQ_blog.html|work=The Washington Post|date=2012-01-19|accessdate=2020-11-21|archive-date=2020-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116193247/https://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/in-the-loop/post/kristy-noem-capitol-hills-most-powerful-intern/2012/01/19/gIQAhujsAQ_blog.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2012年，她获得了[[南达科他州立大学|南达科他州立大学]]政治学学士学位<ref name="degree">{{cite news|first=Seung|last=Min Kim|title=Rep. Kristi Noem earns her bachelor's degree|url=http://www.politico.com/blogs/on-congress/2012/05/rep-kristi-noem-earns-her-bachelors-degree-122659.html|work=[[Politico|Politico]]|date=2012-05-07|access-date=2020-11-21|archive-date=2020-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116193221/https://www.politico.com/blogs/on-congress/2012/05/rep-kristi-noem-earns-her-bachelors-degree-122659|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==南达科他州众议员==
2006年，诺姆在[[南达科他州众议院|南达科他州众议院]]选举中赢得了第6选区（包括[[比德尔县_(南达科他州)|比德尔县]]、[[克拉克县_(南达科他州)|克拉克县]]、[[科丁顿县_(南达科他州)|科丁顿县]]、[[哈姆林县_(南达科他州)|哈姆林县]]和[[金斯伯里县_(南达科他州)|金斯伯里县]]的部分地区，不包括[[沃特敦_(南达科他州)|沃特敦]]）。2006年，她以39％的选票获胜<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ourcampaigns.com/RaceDetail.html?RaceID=301830|title=Our Campaigns - SD State House 06 Race - Nov 07, 2006|website=www.ourcampaigns.com|access-date=2020-12-13|archive-date=2020-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116193224/https://www.ourcampaigns.com/RaceDetail.html?RaceID=301830|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2008年，她以41％的选票再次当选<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ourcampaigns.com/RaceDetail.html?RaceID=434957|title=Our Campaigns - SD State House 06 Race - Nov 04, 2008|website=www.ourcampaigns.com|access-date=2020-12-13|archive-date=2020-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116193247/https://www.ourcampaigns.com/RaceDetail.html?RaceID=434957|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

诺姆从2007年到2010年任职四年，曾担任过多数党领袖助理<ref name="argusleader.com">{{Cite web |url = https://archive.today/20130117210115/http://www.argusleader.com/article/20100609/NEWS/6090318|title = U.S. House: State Rep. Kristi Noem to face Herseth Sandlin in historic clash, Political newcomer beats odds|website=Argus Leader |author = Ellis, Jonathan|date = 2010-06-09|accessdate = 2020-12-13}}</ref><ref name="historical listing">{{cite web|url=http://legis.state.sd.us/historical/LegislatorDetail.aspx?MemberID=3775|title=Kristi Noem|website=South Dakota Legislature Historical Listing|accessdate=2020-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101211105327/http://legis.state.sd.us/historical/LegislatorDetail.aspx?MemberID=3775|archive-date=2010-12-11|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。在2009年和2010年，她发起将南达科他州的义务教育年龄降低到16岁的法案，在此之前的2008年这一年龄被提高到了18岁，而她认为直到18岁仍需要上学并不能提高毕业率<ref name='SDSchoolBoards'>{{cite news | title = Committee stops effort to lower grad age | date = 2010-02-25 | publisher = Associated School Boards of South Dakota | url = http://www.asbsd.org/blog/default.aspx?id=1&category=Student%20Achievement | accessdate = 2020-12-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20101225040917/http://www.asbsd.org/blog/default.aspx?id=1&category=Student%20Achievement | archive-date = 2010-12-25 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。高年龄的支持者认为，此举会提高毕业率，并激励那些原本会辍学的学生<ref name='RCJCook'>{{cite news | first = Andrea | last = Cook | title = Schools step in to rescue dropouts | date = 2010-05-23 | newspaper = Rapid City Journal | url = http://www.rapidcityjournal.com/news/article_bcd51040-704e-11df-81b3-001cc4c03286.html | accessdate = 2020-12-13 | archive-date = 2020-11-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201116193331/https://rapidcityjournal.com/news/article_bcd51040-704e-11df-81b3-001cc4c03286.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

她曾在州事务委员会和税收委员会任职。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ballotpedia.org/wiki/index.php/Kristi_Noem|title=Kristi Noem|website=Ballotpedia|access-date=2020-12-13|archive-date=2012-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120225085134/http://ballotpedia.org/wiki/index.php/Kristi_Noem|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==美国国会众议员==
===任期===
诺姆是第四位在国会代表南达科他州的女性<ref>{{cite news |last=Ellis |first=Jonathan |date=2015-01-06 |title=All GOP delegation first since 1962 |url=http://www.argusleader.com/story/jonathanellis/2015/01/06/gop-delegation-first-since-1962/21332705/ |newspaper=Argus Leader |location=Sioux Falls, South Dakota |accessdate=2020-11-29 |archive-date=2020-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116193218/https://www.argusleader.com/story/jonathanellis/2015/01/06/gop-delegation-first-since-1962/21332705/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她和[[南卡罗来纳州|南卡罗来纳州]]的新任参议员[[蒂姆·斯科特|蒂姆·斯科特]]由2011年众议院共和党87名新任议员以{{le|口头表决|Acclamation}}方式当选为众议院共和党领导层的联络人，从而使诺姆成为众议院共和党领导层的第二位女性成员<ref name='TheHill111710'>{{cite news | first = Michael | last = O'Brien | title = House elects Reps Noem, Scott to leadership | date = 2010-11-17 | publisher = Capitol Hill Publishing Corp. | url = http://thehill.com/blogs/blog-briefing-room/news/129773-house-gop-elects-freshmen-reps-noem-scott-to-leadership | work = The Hill | accessdate = 2020-11-29 | archive-date = 2020-11-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201116193346/https://thehill.com/blogs/blog-briefing-room/news/129773-house-gop-elects-freshmen-reps-noem-scott-to-leadership | dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[国会山报|国会山报]]称，她的职责是推动领导层大幅削减联邦政府开支，并帮助议长[[约翰·博纳|约翰·博纳]]管理新任议员的期望值<ref name='TheHill01012011'>{{cite news | first = Alexander | last = Bolton | title = A new order: House power players to watch in the 112th Congress | date = 2011-01-01 | publisher = Capitol Hill Publishing Corp. | url = http://thehill.com/homenews/house/135581-house-power-players-to-watch-in-the-112th-congress | work = The Hill | accessdate = 2020-11-29 | quote = Noem and Scott ... will give the freshman class a voice in GOP leadership meetings and will press their leaders to take immediate steps to cut government spending significantly. Boehner and other House leaders will also rely on Noem and Scott to manage the expectations of the freshman class. | archive-date = 2020-11-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201116193414/https://thehill.com/homenews/house/135581-house-power-players-to-watch-in-the-112th-congress | dead-url = no }}</ref>
。2011年3月，德克萨斯州共和党众议员[[皮特·赛轩|皮特·赛轩]]在2012年竞选期间提名诺姆为{{le|共和党众议院全国委员会|National Republican Congressional Committee}}的12名地区主任之一<ref name="HeadOfClass"/><ref name='RegDirector'>{{cite news | first = Jessica | last = Brady | title = NRCC Expanding Regional Team in 2012 Noem, Pompeo Among Members With Regions | date = 2011-03-02 | publisher = Congressional Quarterly | url = http://www.rollcall.com/issues/56_89/-203759-1.html | work = Roll Call | accessdate = 2020-11-29 | archive-date = 2018-08-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180811111828/http://www.rollcall.com/issues/56_89/-203759-1.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>

