====医疗保健====
诺姆反对《[[患者保护与平价医疗法案|患者保护与平价医疗法案]]》（奥巴马医改），并投票废除该法案<ref name='NYTObamaCare'>{{cite news | first = David M. | last = Herszenhorn | author2 = Robert Pear | title = House Votes for Repeal of Health Law in Symbolic Act | date = 2011-01-19 | url = https://www.nytimes.com/2011/01/20/health/policy/20cong.html | work = The New York Times | accessdate = 2020-11-29 | archive-date = 2020-11-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201116193346/https://www.nytimes.com/2011/01/20/health/policy/20cong.html | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="wants to stop">{{cite news |url=http://www.ksfy.com/Global/story.asp?S=12711303 |title=GOP House candidate wants to stop Democrat plans |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120323095434/http://www.ksfy.com/Global/story.asp?S=12711303 |archive-date=2012-03-23 |agency=Associated Press |date=2010-06-25 |accessdate=2020-11-29 |work=KSFY-TV |dead-url=no }}</ref>。由于试图废除该法案未获成功，她试图废除该法案的同时保留《印第安医疗保健改善法案》（Indian Health Care Improvement Act），允许父母将其子女的健康保险计划保留到20多岁的条款以及高风险池之类的措施<ref name='NoemHealthCareAlt'>{{cite news | first = David | last = Montgomery | title = Noem, Republicans say replacement health care proposals on the way | date = 2011-01-20 | publisher = Lee Enterprises | url = http://www.rapidcityjournal.com/news/article_245dea88-2504-11e0-b431-001cc4c03286.html | work = Rapid City Journal | accessdate = 2020-11-29 | archive-date = 2020-11-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201116193320/https://rapidcityjournal.com/news/article_245dea88-2504-11e0-b431-001cc4c03286.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。诺姆希望在联邦法律中增加的新条款包括限制[[医疗事故|医疗事故]]诉讼，允许患者从其他州购买医疗保险计划<ref name='NoemHealthCareAlt'/>。她支持共和党预算委员会主席[[保罗·莱恩|保罗·莱恩]]提出的削减[[联邦医疗补助|联邦医疗补助]]资金的提议，这将使[[南达科他州|南达科他州]]的福利医疗补助对象减少55%<ref name='NoemJoinsThune'>{{cite news | first = Denise | last = Ross | title = South Dakota Rep. Noem joins Thune in opposing end to oil tax breaks | date = 2011-05-13 | url = http://www.mitchellrepublic.com/event/article/id/52593/ | work = Mitchell Republic | accessdate = 2020-11-29 }}{{Dead link}}</ref>。

====社会问题====
诺姆反对堕胎<ref name="long after">{{Cite web|url = http://www.rapidcityjournal.com/news/article_1f959980-2418-11df-affd-001cc4c002e0.html|title = Long after abortion wars, resentment toward Chris Nelson lingers|website = Rapid City Journal|author = Woster, Kevin|date = 2010-03-01|language = en|accessdate = 2020-11-29|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201116193323/https://rapidcityjournal.com/news/article_1f959980-2418-11df-affd-001cc4c002e0.html|archive-date = 2020-11-16|dead-url = no}}</ref>。她得到了[[反堕胎|反堕胎]]组织{{le|Susan B. Anthony List|Susan B. Anthony List}}的支持<ref name="pro-life">{{cite news |last=Hollingsworth |first=Barbara |date=2010-06-15 |access-date=2020-11-29 |title=Pro-life women take political center stage |url=https://www.sfexaminer.com/opinion/barbara-hollingsworth-pro-life-women-take-political-center-stage/ |newspaper=San Francisco Examiner |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200518213205/https://www.sfexaminer.com/opinion/barbara-hollingsworth-pro-life-women-take-political-center-stage/ |archive-date=2020-05-18 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，她在当选后表示，她希望在2018年6月保持她从SBA List获得的100%反堕胎投票记录<ref name=BendavidWSJ>{{cite news | first = Naftali | last = Bendavid | title = GOP Elevates Some New Faces | date = 2010-11-18 | publisher = Dow Jones | url = https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB10001424052748703688704575621071505176634 | work = The Wall Street Journal | accessdate = 2020-11-29 | archive-date = 2020-11-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201116193325/https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB10001424052748703688704575621071505176634 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|date=2018-06-06|title=SBA List Declares Victory as Rep. Kristi Noem Wins Primary for Governor of South Dakota|url=https://www.sba-list.org/newsroom/press-releases/sba-list-declares-victory-rep-kristi-noem-wins-primary-governor-south-dakota|access-date=2020-11-29|website=Susan B. Anthony List|archive-date=2020-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201211110551/https://www.sba-list.org/newsroom/press-releases/sba-list-declares-victory-rep-kristi-noem-wins-primary-governor-south-dakota|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

