诺姆说，美国必须结束对{{le|美国能源独立|United States energy independence|外国石油}}的依赖。为了实现这一目标，她说，国会应该鼓励保护现有资源<ref name='KeolandEnergy'>{{cite news|title=Noem: SD Needs Better Energy Policy|date=2011-03-03|url=http://www.keloland.com/News/NewsDetail6376.cfm?Id=111667|work=KELO-TV|accessdate=2020-12-02|dead-url=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110311230710/http://www.keloland.com/News/NewsDetail6376.cfm?Id=111667|archivedate=2011-03-11}}</ref>，她支持继续向本州提供[[乙醇|乙醇]]补贴<ref>{{cite news |last1=Workman |first1=Kurtis |title=New South Dakota Congresswoman Say Ethanol Subsidy Good For Recovery |url=http://plainsdaily.com/entry/new_south_dakota_congresswoman_say_ethanol_subsidy_good_for_recovery/ |accessdate=2020-12-02 |work=PlainsDaily.com |date=2010-12-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101213064653/http://plainsdaily.com/entry/new_south_dakota_congresswoman_say_ethanol_subsidy_good_for_recovery/ |archivedate=2010-12-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref> ，并反对终止联邦对石油公司的补贴<ref name="NoemJoinsThune"/>。

