诺姆反对南达科他州国会参议员[[提姆·约翰逊|提姆·约翰逊]]提出的一项法案，该法案将48,000英亩（190平方公里）的{{le|水牛沟国家草原|Buffalo Gap National Grassland}}指定为[[国家荒野保护体系|受保护的荒野]]<ref>{{cite news|last=Woster|first=Kevin|title=Noem continues assault on Johnson wilderness plan|url=http://www.rapidcityjournal.com/news/local/article_f5b47084-bc7c-11df-9295-001cc4c002e0.html|accessdate=2020-12-02|newspaper=Rapid City Journal|date=2010-09-09|archive-date=2020-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116193224/https://rapidcityjournal.com/news/local/article_f5b47084-bc7c-11df-9295-001cc4c002e0.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她支持目前将这片土地指定为[[美国国家草原|国家草原]]<ref name='BuffaloGap03202011'>{{cite news | first = Kevin | last = Woster | title = Rough road ahead in Congress for Johnson wilderness plan | date = 2011-03-20 | url = http://www.rapidcityjournal.com/news/article_aa215058-5298-11e0-b4c0-001cc4c03286.html | work = Rapid City Journal | accessdate = 2020-12-02 | quote = Noem made opposition to Johnson's wilderness plan one of her prominent campaign points last year in her race against incumbent Rep. Stephanie Herseth Sandlin, a Democrat. | archive-date = 2020-11-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201116193314/https://rapidcityjournal.com/news/article_aa215058-5298-11e0-b4c0-001cc4c03286.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。她指出，土地已经被管理为类似于荒野的无路区域<ref name='BuffaloGapAL09102011'>{{cite news | first = Jonathan | last = Ellis | title = Kristi Noem's stance on Buffalo Gap draws ire from unexpected source | date = 2010-10-09 | publisher = [[Gannett|Gannett]] | url = http://www.argusleader.com/article/20100910/NEWS/9100324/Kristi-Noem-s-stance-Buffalo-Gap-draws-ire-from-unexpected-source | work = Sioux Falls Argus Leader | accessdate = 2020-12-02 | quote = Noem ... said Thursday the current management system preserves the land without threatening leaseholder options. | dead-url = yes | archiveurl = https://archive.is/20130117221728/http://www.argusleader.com/article/20100910/NEWS/9100324/Kristi-Noem-s-stance-Buffalo-Gap-draws-ire-from-unexpected-source | archivedate = 2013-01-17 }}</ref>，并指出将土地指定为荒野将进一步限制承租人获得土地并危及{{le|放牧权|Grazing rights}}<ref name='BuffaloGap03202011'/><ref name='BuffaloGapAL09102011'/>。

诺姆支持{{le|离岸钻井|Offshore drilling|近海石油开采}}<ref name='JournalOffshore'>{{cite news | title = Noem seeks off-shore oil drilling | date = 2011-04-01 | newspaper = Rapid City Journal | url = http://www.rapidcityjournal.com/news/article_1c8d892e-5bf7-11e0-a149-001cc4c03286.html | accessdate = 2020-12-02 | archive-date = 2020-11-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201116193318/https://rapidcityjournal.com/news/article_1c8d892e-5bf7-11e0-a149-001cc4c03286.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。她共同发起了三项法案，她认为，终止2010年美国在[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]的{{le|2010年美国深水钻井暂停令|2010 United States deepwater drilling moratorium|深水钻井暂停令}}，以及在{{le|墨西哥湾的海上石油和天然气 (美国)|Offshore oil and gas in the Gulf of Mexico (United States)|墨西哥湾}}和{{le|美国大西洋沿岸的近海钻探|Offshore drilling on the Atlantic coast of the United States|弗吉尼亚海岸附近}}重新开放石油租赁销售将减少美国对外国石油的依赖<ref name='FoxTVOffshore'>{{cite news |title=Noem wants to expand offshore energy production |date=2011-03-31 |publisher=Black Hills FOX |url=http://www.blackhillsfox.com/2011/03/31/Noem-wants-to-expand-offshore-energy-production |accessdate=2020-12-02 |quote=The bills would end the Obama administration's moratorium on drilling in the Gulf of Mexico and require the re-opening of sales on oil leases in the Gulf and off the coast of Virginia. |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111003162923/http://www.blackhillsfox.com/2011/03/31/Noem-wants-to-expand-offshore-energy-production |archivedate=2011-10-03 }}</ref>。2011年，她发起了一项措施，以阻止[[美国国家环境保护局|美国国家环境保护局]]对[[颗粒物|粗颗粒物]]实行更严格的[[空气污染|空气污染]]标准<ref>{{cite web |first=Sue |last=Sturgis |url=https://www.facingsouth.org/2011/02/house-votes-to-halt-strict-coal-ash-rules-but-fight-will-continue-in-senate.html |title=House votes to halt strict coal ash rules, but fight will continue in Senate |work=Facing South |publisher=Institute for Southern Studies |date=2011-02-21 |access-date=2020-12-02 |archive-date=2020-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116193225/https://www.facingsouth.org/2011/02/house-votes-to-halt-strict-coal-ash-rules-but-fight-will-continue-in-senate.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

====外交====
诺姆支持[[2011年多国武装干涉利比亚|北约领导的军事干预]][[利比亚内战_(2011年)|2011年利比亚内战]]，但质疑美国干预是为了保护平民，还是试图赶走时任领导人[[穆阿迈尔·卡扎菲|卡扎菲]]<ref name='Gaddafi'>{{cite news | first = David | last = Montgomery | title = Thune, Noem want answers on Libya | date = 2010-03-24 | url = http://www.rapidcityjournal.com/news/article_57540f4e-562d-11e0-9f87-001cc4c03286.html | work = Rapid City Journal | accessdate = 2020-12-07 | archive-date = 2020-11-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201116193346/https://rapidcityjournal.com/news/article_57540f4e-562d-11e0-9f87-001cc4c03286.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。同年3月，她呼吁[[奥巴马|奥巴马]]总统提供更多关于美国在冲突中所扮演角色的信息，并称奥巴马的声明含糊和模棱两可<ref name='Gaddafi' /><ref name='WischmeyerLibya'>{{Cite web | last = Wischmeyer | first = Beth | title = Reaction to speech splits along party lines | location = Sioux Falls, South Dakota | newspaper = Argus Leader | date = 2011-03-29 | url = http://www.argusleader.com/article/20110329/NEWS/103290326/1001/1-5-bridges-state-deficient/Reaction-speech-splits-along-party-lines | accessdate = 2020-12-07 | dead-url = yes | archiveurl = https://archive.today/20130117053501/http://www.argusleader.com/article/20110329/NEWS/103290326/1001/1-5-bridges-state-deficient/Reaction-speech-splits-along-party-lines?odyssey=nav | archivedate = 2013-01-17 }}</ref>。

====筹款====
自当选以来，诺姆筹集的捐款包括56%的个人捐款和44%的政治行动委员会捐款<ref name="record pace">{{cite web|title = Noem raises money for campaign at record pace|url = http://www.rapidcityjournal.com/news/article_960819ac-6568-11e0-be5b-001cc4c002e0.html|website = Rapid City Journal|date = 2011-04-12|access-date = 2020-12-07|archive-date = 2020-11-16|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201116193336/https://rapidcityjournal.com/news/article_960819ac-6568-11e0-be5b-001cc4c002e0.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>。2011年3月8日，她宣布成立一个领导[[政治行动委员会|政治行动委员会]]——克里斯蒂政治行动委员会（KRISTI PAC），并表示她将利用PAC支付费用以及支持其他共和党候选人。南达科他州前{{le|南达科他州副州长|Lieutenant Governor of South Dakota|副州长}}{{le|史蒂夫·柯比|Steve T. Kirby}}是其财务主管<ref name="PACFormed">{{cite news|author=Journal Staff|title=Noem starts leadership PAC|date=2011-03-08|publisher=Lee Enterprises|url=http://www.rapidcityjournal.com/news/article_c3f7db96-49f1-11e0-bda5-001cc4c002e0.html|work=Rapid City Journal|accessdate=2020-12-07|archive-date=2020-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116193358/https://rapidcityjournal.com/news/article_c3f7db96-49f1-11e0-bda5-001cc4c002e0.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="freshman forming">{{cite news | first = Derek | last = Willis | title = G.O.P. Freshmen Forming Leadership PACs | date = 2011-03-08 | url = http://thecaucus.blogs.nytimes.com/2011/03/08/gop-freshmen-forming-leadership-pacs/?partner=rss&emc=rss | work = The New York Times | accessdate = 2020-12-07 | archive-date = 2020-11-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201116193322/https://thecaucus.blogs.nytimes.com/2011/03/08/gop-freshmen-forming-leadership-pacs/?partner=rss&emc=rss | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name='PoliticoPAC'>{{cite news|first=Alex|last=Isenstadt|title=Freshmen enroll in PACs 101|date=2011-03-15|url=http://www.politico.com/news/stories/0311/51290.html|work=POLITICO|accessdate=2020-12-07|archive-date=2020-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116193402/https://www.politico.com/story/2011/03/freshmen-enroll-in-pacs-101-051290|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

诺姆是2011年第一季度共和党新人在PAC筹款活动中的佼佼者，她从PACs筹集了16.9万美元，并主持了至少10次华盛顿筹款活动<ref name="influence industry">{{cite web |url= https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/the-influence-industry/2011/04/20/AFNKReEE_print.html |title= The Influence Industry: New Republicans play an old fundraising game |author= T.W. Farnam |date= 2011-04-20 |website= The Washington Post |accessdate= 2020-12-07 |archive-date= 2020-11-16 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201116193342/https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/the-influence-industry/2011/04/20/AFNKReEE_print.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>。她表示，她没有加入众议院{{le|茶党核心小组|Tea Party Caucus}}的计划<ref name="MiddleGround">{{cite web |url= http://www.argusleader.com/fdcp/?unique=1303756814318 |title= Kristi Noem finds patches of middle ground |author= Ledyard King |date= 2011-04-25 |website= Sioux Falls Argus Leader |accessdate= 2020-12-07 }}{{Dead link}}</ref>。

====移民和难民====
诺姆支持特朗普总统2017年的[[第13769号行政命令|行政命令]]，该命令将美国难民计划暂停120天，并禁止7个[[穆斯林|穆斯林]]占多数的国家的国民前往美国90天<ref name="Ferguson">{{cite news |first=Dana |last=Ferguson |url=http://www.argusleader.com/story/news/politics/2017/01/29/rep-noem-supports-suspending-us-refugee-program/97229434/ |title=Rep. Noem supports suspending U.S. refugee program |newspaper=Argus Leader |date=2017-01-29 |access-date=2020-12-02 |archive-date=2020-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116193213/https://www.argusleader.com/story/news/politics/2017/01/29/rep-noem-supports-suspending-us-refugee-program/97229434/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她说，她支持临时禁止接受来自“[[恐怖分子|恐怖分子]]控制”地区的难民<ref name="Blake1">{{cite web|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/the-fix/wp/2017/01/29/heres-where-republicans-stand-on-president-trumps-controversial-travel-ban|title=Whip Count: Here's where Republicans stand on Trump's controversial travel ban|last1=Blake|first1=Aaron|date=2017-01-31|newspaper=The Washington Post|access-date=2017-04-07|archive-date=2020-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116193256/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/the-fix/wp/2017/01/29/heres-where-republicans-stand-on-president-trumps-controversial-travel-ban|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但没有说明她是否支持该命令的其他方面，这项命令可能导致合法的美国居民，如绿卡持有者和具有[[双重国籍|双重国籍]]的人在重新入境时被拘留<ref name="Ferguson" />。

==南达科他州州长==
===2018年选举===
2016年11月14日，诺姆宣布，她不会寻求连任国会议员，而是在{{le|2018年南达科他州州长选举|2018 South Dakota gubernatorial election|2018年}}竞选{{le|南达科他州州长|Governor of South Dakota|州长}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.politico.com/story/2016/11/kristi-noem-south-dakota-231386|title=Rep. Kristi Noem to run for South Dakota governor|work=Politico|date=2016-11-14|accessdate=2020-11-22|archive-date=2020-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116193226/https://www.politico.com/story/2016/11/kristi-noem-south-dakota-231386|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她在6月5日的初选中以56%对44%的优势击败现任南达科他州司法部长{{le|马蒂·杰克利|Marty Jackley}}<ref name="SDSOS06062018">{{cite web |url=http://electionresults.sd.gov/resultsSW.aspx?type=SWR&map=CTY |title=State of South Dakota Secretary of State Official Election Results |date=2018-06-05 |access-date=2020-11-22 |archive-date=2019-03-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190330070533/http://electionresults.sd.gov/resultsSW.aspx?type=SWR&map=CTY |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.foxnews.com/politics/2018/06/06/rep-kristi-noem-wins-south-dakota-gop-governor-primary.html |title=Rep. Kristi Noem wins South Dakota GOP governor primary |work=FOX News |date=2018-06-06 |accessdate=2020-11-22 |archive-date=2018-08-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180816202444/http://www.foxnews.com/politics/2018/06/06/rep-kristi-noem-wins-south-dakota-gop-governor-primary.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，并在大选中以51%比47.6%击败[[民主党_(美国)|民主党]]提名人{{le|比利·萨顿|Billie Sutton}}<ref name="South Dakota Election Results">{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2018/11/06/us/elections/results-south-dakota-elections.html|title=South Dakota Election Results|date=2018-11-06|work=The New York Times|access-date=2020-11-22|language=en-US|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2020-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116193238/https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2018/11/06/us/elections/results-south-dakota-elections.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===任期===
诺姆于2019年1月5日宣誓就任南达科他州州长。她是南达科他州历史上首位担任这一职务的女性。<ref>{{cite news |first=James |last=Nord |url=https://apnews.com/cde32361793e40cea06dc270794b57e8 |title=Kristi Noem sworn in as South Dakota's 1st female governor |agency=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]] |date=2019-01-05 |access-date=2020-11-22 |archive-date=2020-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116193225/https://apnews.com/cde32361793e40cea06dc270794b57e8 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

