====婚姻====
作为家庭优先倡议的一部分，诺姆承诺保护宗教自由和传统婚姻。她将婚姻描述为“上帝赐予的一男一女的结合”，并将最高法院的判决称为试图让那些戴着传统腰带的人保持沉默。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Kristi for Governor|url=https://kristiforgovernor.com/|access-date=2020-12-16|website=Kristi for Governor|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201215041451/https://kristiforgovernor.com/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

====堕胎====
2019年3月20日，诺姆签署了一项法案，要求南达科他州的[[州立大学|州立大学]]促进和保护知识多样性<ref>{{cite news | last1=Ellis | first1=Jonathan | title=Noem, GOP target university 'political correctness' with first-of-its-kind diversity, speech law | url=https://www.argusleader.com/story/news/2019/03/20/gov-kristi-noem-gop-target-university-political-correctness-south-dakota-legislature-free-speech/3226155002/ | date=2019-03-20 | newspaper=Argus Leader | accessdate=2020-11-22 | archive-date=2020-11-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116193230/https://www.argusleader.com/story/news/2019/03/20/gov-kristi-noem-gop-target-university-political-correctness-south-dakota-legislature-free-speech/3226155002/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>，同一天，她签署了几项限制堕胎的法案。诺姆说，这些法案将“打击南达科他州的堕胎提供者”，要求堕胎者在结束妊娠前必须签署州表格。她还说，“强大而不断发展的医学研究提供了证据，证明未出生的婴儿可以在子宫里感觉、思考和识别声音。他们都是人，必须给予他们与其他人同样的基本尊严。”<ref>{{cite web | last1=Kaczke | first1=Lisa | title=Gov. Kristi Noem signs pro-life bills into law | url=https://www.argusleader.com/story/news/politics/2019/03/20/gov-kristi-noem-signs-pro-life-bills-into-law/3227694002/ | date=2019-03-20 | newspaper=Argus Leader | accessdate=2020-11-22 | archive-date=2020-11-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116193227/https://www.argusleader.com/story/news/politics/2019/03/20/gov-kristi-noem-signs-pro-life-bills-into-law/3227694002/ | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title=South Dakota governor signs bills aimed at curbing abortion | url=https://abcnews.go.com/US/wireStory/south-dakota-governor-signs-bills-aimed-curbing-abortion-61853868 | date=2019-03-20 | publisher=ABC News | accessdate=2020-11-22 | archive-date=2020-11-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116193236/https://abcnews.go.com/US/wireStory/south-dakota-governor-signs-bills-aimed-curbing-abortion-61853868 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

====贸易====
2019年2月，诺姆称[[唐纳德·特朗普|特朗普]]政府的贸易战摧毁了南达科他州经济，尤其是农业部门。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://politi.co/2Iw6mH5|title=South Dakota governor says Trump trade wars have 'devastated' the state|last=Oprysko|first=Caitlin|website=POLITICO|language=en|access-date=2020-11-22|archive-date=2020-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116193231/https://www.politico.com/story/2019/02/22/trump-trade-south-dakota-1180196|dead-url=no}}</ref>

