====COVID-19大流行====
在{{le|南达科他州COVID-19大流行|COVID-19 pandemic in South Dakota}}期间，诺姆采取了一种不干涉的方法<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=South Dakota governor uses coronavirus relief funds for $5 million tourism ad despite COVID surge|url=https://www.cbsnews.com/news/kristi-noem-south-dakota-coronavirus-relief-funds-tourism/|access-date=2020-11-25|website=www.cbsnews.com|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116193232/https://www.cbsnews.com/news/kristi-noem-south-dakota-coronavirus-relief-funds-tourism/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。截至2020年4月14日，她是七位尚未发布全州[[居家令|居家令]]的州长之一<ref>{{cite news | last1=Beaumont | first1=Thomas | last2=Groves | first2=Stephen | title='A resume for future office': Virus tests a GOP governor | url=https://apnews.com/5fd99698995959a4ac3fe88625732367 | date=2020-05-05 | agency=Associated Press | accessdate=2020-11-25 | archive-date=2020-11-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116193240/https://apnews.com/5fd99698995959a4ac3fe88625732367 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。她强调了她所在州在评估[[羟氯喹|羟氯喹]]，一种[[抗疟药|抗疟药]]在治疗COVID-19方面的作用，而之后的部分研究表明其无效<ref name=":2" /><ref name=":3">{{Cite news|date=2020-07-29|title=Coronavirus: Hydroxychloroquine ineffective says Fauci|language=en-GB|work=BBC News|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-us-canada-53575964|access-date=2020-11-25|archive-date=2020-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128214117/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-us-canada-53575964|dead-url=no}}</ref>。美国总统[[唐纳德·特朗普|特朗普]]曾经大力推广了这种药物<ref name=":2">{{Cite news |url=https://www.cnn.com/2020/04/14/politics/south-dakota-governor-kristi-noem-coronavirus/index.html |title=South Dakota governor faces criticism over refusal to issue stay-at-home order after pork plant outbreak |last=Bradner |first=Eric |date=2020-04-14 |work=CNN |access-date=2020-11-25 |archive-date=2020-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116193234/https://www.cnn.com/2020/04/14/politics/south-dakota-governor-kristi-noem-coronavirus/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=":3" />。

7月3日，在[[拉什莫尔山|拉什莫尔山]]，特朗普参加了一个活动，诺姆没有要求社交距离或戴[[口罩|口罩]]<ref name="auto">{{Cite news |last=Cummings |first=William |title='We won't be social distancing' at Mount Rushmore celebration with Trump, says SD Gov. Noem |url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2020/07/01/kristi-noem-social-distancing-mount-rushmore-trump/5354257002/ |access-date=2020-11-25 |newspaper=USA Today |language=en-US |date=2020-07-01 |archive-date=2020-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116193236/https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2020/07/01/kristi-noem-social-distancing-mount-rushmore-trump/5354257002/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。诺姆对有关口罩在减缓[[SARS-CoV-2|SARS-CoV-2]]传播中的作用表示怀疑<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|date=2020-10-22|title=Noem says South Dakota is doing 'good' as virus surges|url=https://apnews.com/article/virus-outbreak-health-south-dakota-f967a1a56b798f43ae0d2be971b27b39|access-date=2020-11-25|website=AP NEWS|archive-date=2020-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116193231/https://apnews.com/article/virus-outbreak-health-south-dakota-f967a1a56b798f43ae0d2be971b27b39|dead-url=no}}</ref>。诺姆在为自己对口罩的看法解释时，引用了一个保守的医学组织——{{le|美国内科和外科医生协会|Association of American Physicians and Surgeons}}的主张，该组织因反对{{le|COVID-19大流行封锁|COVID-19 pandemic lockdowns}}而闻名<ref name=":0" />。

===总统选举人===
2020年6月20日，在共和党州代表大会上，诺姆被选为南达科他州三名共和党总统选举人之一，其他两位分别是副州长{{le|拉里·罗登|Larry Rhoden}}和司法部长{{le|杰森·拉文斯堡|Jason Ravnsborg}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://southdakotagopconvention.com/results/|title=Convention Results|publisher=southdakotagopconvention.com|date=2020-06-20|accessdate=2020-11-25|archive-date=2020-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116193309/https://southdakotagopconvention.com/results/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。12月12日，南达科他州共和党主席{{le|丹·莱德曼|Dan Lederman}}宣布将接替诺姆成为选举人<ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-12-13|title=Lederman in, Noem out as S.D. Trump elector|url=https://www.keloland.com/news/capitol-news-bureau/lederman-in-noem-out-as-s-d-trump-elector/|access-date=2020-12-20|website=KELOLAND|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201225221825/https://www.keloland.com/news/capitol-news-bureau/lederman-in-noem-out-as-s-d-trump-elector/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==个人生活==
诺姆和她的丈夫以及三个孩子住在[[卡斯尔伍德_(南达科他州)|卡斯尔伍德]]附近的拉科塔山谷牧场（Racota Valley Ranch）上。

诺姆已经收到26张交通罚单，包括1989年至2010年的20张超速罚单<ref>{{Cite news |last=Yingling |first=Jennifer |date=2010-08-27 |title='Please pull over': GOP candidate has 26 traffic violations |url=https://thehill.com/blogs/in-the-know/in-the-know/254343-please-pull-over-gop-candidate-has-26-traffic-violations |access-date=2020-11-25 |newspaper=The Hill |language=en |archive-date=2020-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116193332/https://thehill.com/blogs/in-the-know/in-the-know/254343-please-pull-over-gop-candidate-has-26-traffic-violations |dead-url=no }}</ref>，违反停车标志和安全带的规定，无驾驶执照，{{le|未出庭|Failure to appear}}和两项[[逮捕令|逮捕令]]。她说：“我不为自己的驾驶记录感到骄傲，但我一直在努力为年轻人和年轻驾驶员树立一个更好的榜样。”她已经接受了罚款在内的处罚。<ref>{{Cite news |last=Woster |first=Kevin |title=Life in the too-fast lane: Noem traffic shows long list of tickets |url=https://rapidcityjournal.com/news/life-in-the-too-fast-lane-noem-traffic-shows-long-list-of-tickets/article_5fdda8ca-b18a-11df-8518-001cc4c002e0.html |date=2010-08-27 |access-date=2020-11-25 |website=Rapid City Journal |language=en |archive-date=2020-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116193323/https://rapidcityjournal.com/news/life-in-the-too-fast-lane-noem-traffic-shows-long-list-of-tickets/article_5fdda8ca-b18a-11df-8518-001cc4c002e0.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Noem's driving record takes wheel of campaign|url=https://www.mitchellrepublic.com/news/government-and-politics/1528437-noems-driving-record-takes-wheel-campaign|access-date=2020-11-25|website=The Mitchell Republic|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116193422/https://www.mitchellrepublic.com/news/government-and-politics/1528437-noems-driving-record-takes-wheel-campaign|dead-url=no}}</ref>

